data.description: Welcome to Skyborne, a beautiful community with lots to offer including low hoa, dog park, tot lot, and community pool. This home is one of the largest models in the development with 2009 sq ft with 3 bedrooms and 2 ½ baths. Neutral tile and laminate floors throughout along with plantation shutters. This home features OWNED and PAID for SOLAR, and per the seller covers the entire electric bill.  A large open entertainers' kitchen with granite countertops overlooking the great room with fireplace. A separate family or dining room, plus an enclosed patio off the kitchen area that makes a great office space. The over 9500+ sqft backyard and outdoor area is one of the largest lots in the neighborhood and perfect for creating your own personal paradise. This home is a must see! More photos coming soon.
